    <h1>About</h1>

    <p>This site is maintained by Rui Vasconcelos. The work collected here develops <em>optimisation blindness</em> as a conceptual frame, <em>RevEmo</em> as a property-level measurement framework, and <em>DEQI</em> as a destination-level measurement framework, alongside essays exploring how the concept surfaces in practice.</p>

    <p>Rui leads Altavella, a hospitality investment and advisory firm working with owners, operators, investors, and destination authorities across Europe and the Middle East. The work on this site is intellectual and academic. It is published separately from Altavella's commercial activity and is intended to be read, cited, and challenged on its own terms.</p>

    <p>Correspondence is welcome at <a href="mailto:vasconcelos@altavella.com">vasconcelos@altavella.com</a>. Citations, corrections, and substantive disagreement are particularly welcome. The frameworks developed here will improve faster against careful objection than against polite agreement.</p>
  </article>
